12
00:02:29,517 --> 00:02:31,155
Medina is to the north

13
00:02:31,185 --> 00:02:33,971
They made the tracks, not I

14
00:02:34,021 --> 00:02:36,876
Know much? Traveling West?

15
00:02:37,024 --> 00:02:38,945
I know my art

16
00:02:38,991 --> 00:02:42,176
