17
00:02:45,897 --> 00:02:46,921
we go with him

18
00:03:02,911 --> 00:03:04,799
he may be in that cave over there

19
00:03:09,550 --> 00:03:14,475
Muhammad, if you come out, we will
take you to Mecca alive

20
00:03:28,298 --> 00:03:29,014
Muhammad, come out

21
