45
00:08:41,020 --> 00:08:41,782
Clever man!

46
00:08:41,788 --> 00:08:45,303
A choice made by camel
can offend no one

47
00:10:09,192 --> 00:10:10,910
Here we will build the house of the Prophet

48
00:10:13,529 --> 00:10:16,680
And our first meeting place,
a prayer house

49
00:10:18,634 --> 00:10:20,919
the first mosque of Islam, here!

50
00:10:23,238 --> 00:10:26,263
God is great!
God is great!

51
00:11:02,803 --> 00:11:06,193
What's got the prophet to start doing it?
carrying bricks?

52
00:11:06,239 --> 00:11:16,340
Give me that Look, you are doing too much,
please go and sit down we will do it

53
