But they are led by greed, we are
led by god and you

115
00:20:28,298 --> 00:20:36,033
I know how you hate the sword, but
we have to fight

116
00:20:41,409 --> 00:20:49,008
they've stolen our property, they are taking it to Damascus

117
00:20:49,016 --> 00:20:55,852
right past our own door our door.
I say, by God turn back

118
00:21:19,207 --> 00:21:20,925
I'm sorry I got carried away

119
00:21:23,543 --> 00:21:25,226
Its pounding in my head

120
00:21:28,447 --> 00:21:32,235
Please, fight them!

121
00:22:13,651 --> 00:22:15,801
But look at the sun!

122
00:22:24,994 --> 00:22:26,484
It's not the time of prayer

123
00:22:51,315 --> 00:22:56,035
It is newly revealed by god to his messenger

124
00:22:58,087 --> 00:23:02,546
Fight, but fight in the way of god
against those who fight against you

125
00:23:03,659 --> 00:23:06,002
Drive them out of the places from where they drove you out,


126
00:23:06,028 --> 00:23:08,860
for persecution is worse than slaughter

127
00:23:10,031 --> 00:23:14,945
Fight them until persecution is no more

128
00:23:14,968 --> 00:23:20,132
and religion is God,
but if they stop, let there be no more war

129
00:23:21,640 --> 00:23:26,315
for god never loves the slaughters of wars

130
00:23:26,344 --> 00:23:30,814
so, fight in the way of god
against those who fight against you

131
00:23:32,182 --> 00:23:38,950
God is great!
God is great!
God is great!
God is great!

132
00:24:21,089 --> 00:24:25,161
These are the disciplines that the Prophet
puts upon you

133
00:24:25,792 --> 00:24:31,491
you may not harm a woman, a child or any old person! 

134
00:24:32,732 --> 00:24:35,803
you may not harm cripples

135
00:24:35,834 --> 00:24:39,543
you may not harm the man that works in the field

136
00:24:40,437 --> 00:24:43,281
You may not cut down trees

137
00:24:44,575 --> 00:24:47,407
Strike only at those who have expelled you

138
00:24:48,511 --> 00:24:52,503
who have stolen your rights and
riched themselves with your possession!

139
00:24:59,420 --> 00:25:03,765
now, to the wells of Badr

140
00:25:12,431 --> 00:25:14,933
News from Medina!

141
00:25:14,999 --> 00:25:20,152
Arms... Arm yourself... Arm yourself...

142
00:25:20,303 --> 00:25:23,283
defend your wealth

143
00:25:23,939 --> 00:25:25,292
Muhammad has come out of Medina to attack the great caravan

144
00:25:25,641 --> 00:25:28,485
