20 of mine with wine..
we will make a feast of it

148
00:25:39,620 --> 00:25:41,371
That is a war I'd like to fight

149
00:25:42,021 --> 00:25:44,410
a war we can not lose!

150
00:26:28,193 --> 00:26:31,184
ride to Abu Sufian's caravan.
tell him to turn towards Badr

151
00:26:31,361 --> 00:26:33,784
We will join forces tomorrow
near sources of Beder

152
00:27:29,676 --> 00:27:36,637
Wells of Badr... here

153
