I don't like it

157
00:28:00,401 --> 00:28:03,790
There is too much of Mecca on my caravan to be risked

158
00:28:07,474 --> 00:28:11,170
put out the fires...
hold the camels...

159
00:28:20,884 --> 00:28:23,762
