and the future will look after itself

178
00:31:53,025 --> 00:31:55,413
Utbah is not a coward

179
00:32:00,564 --> 00:32:05,318
we will finish them tomorrow. 
We fight! we fight!

180
00:32:43,999 --> 00:32:45,045
are you finished?

181
